  "summary": "Package exfiltrates data to Telegram Bot API",
  "details": "The file 66o.js (lines 31 and 34) contains hardcoded calls to api.telegram.org/bot.../sendMessage with a chat_id parameter, a well-known pattern for exfiltrating data to an attacker-controlled Telegram channel. The package name '8oo' is generic/opaque with no legitimate purpose disclosed that would justify hardcoding a Telegram bot token and chat_id. Any data supplied to or collected by this module is silently relayed to the hardcoded Telegram chat, constituting installer-side harm (credential/data exfiltration channel baked into normal code paths).",
